                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p>
                                <span class="theme-text">9. </span>
                                Eco-Chemical Corp is creating a charter to implement quality practices and standards at all of its manufacturing facilities to ensure they comply with OSHA Star Site requirements. Each of the plant managers has specified requirements regarding scope, resources, and cost. Completion dates for work at each facility have been included in the charter. These dates
                            </p>
                            <ul>
