                        <div>
                            <p>
                                <span class="theme-text">21. </span>The team is evaluating the identified risks and is using several techniques. Which of the following does not include an estimate of the degree of risk as part of the estimating technique?
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>A. Program Evaluation and Review Technique</li>
