                            <p>
                                <span class="theme-text">22. </span>The project manager and her team are finalizing their risk response plans and have evaluated three risks with an impact in excess of $50,000 each. One risk will be outsourced, insurance will offset the second risk and the team will partner with the QC department to manage the third risk. In addition, twelve risks have been logged on the watch list and are considered actively accepted. What is the team’s next step?
