                                <li>C. Update the charter to reflect the agreed upon changes and meet with the three vice presidents to achieve final buy-in</li>
                                <li>D. Call a meeting to present the completed plan, including the approved scope, schedule and cost plans to the eight key stakeholders for final approval</li>
