                        <div>
                            <p>
                                <span class="theme-text">26. </span>You are reviewing your processes to ensure that you and the team are following the plan exactly as stated. When you look at the reports for the past six weeks, you notice that four of your team members are consistently a day late in completing deliverables. You are looking for a tool which you can ask the team to use to link the late deliverables to the team members’ actions. Which of the following will best help in this effort?
